  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0192c7cd-f8e3-46c8-af28-15b04c532e12\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d2732a37-3ad4-4357-8c54-27e70375cc5e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ebae0340-ea39-4cca-be06-6267fb1789e0\"><b>안녕하세요 사당동 한의원 </b></span><span style=\"background-color:#fff593;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0a91e6c3-3f00-439d-ba02-dc58bbd60b9e\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ae997e09-ab46-4486-bff6-0fabcb56fa3d\"><b>입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-0192c7cd-f8e3-46c8-af28-15b04c532e12\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d28a3718-dcd8-46fa-a0b6-89287ec853a5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"2\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_2.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c167d221-9184-4df2-8eb7-680a0082c21e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a3ad7843-0b14-4930-a936-d27dde48e083\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0eda4898-1c4b-4fe6-9cc1-2fceec0211cf\">나이가 들면서 “이름이 생각이 안 나네”, “물건을 어디에 뒀더라?” </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-52ae9ca7-2a35-432c-a8c3-c6df426ac1aa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d461c305-94e2-4b43-8437-1be4c5f6ec4a\">하는 순간이 잦아질 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5ccda874-8011-470c-87de-eb335acdf5a0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a2083d37-31ac-4694-9f97-94f5736db39d\">하지만 단순한 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4d6fe4eb-78a9-46f8-a787-cc3acd512595\"><b>건망증</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-524ddd9d-d79a-4ab3-ab69-6068860e671a\">과 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f355d59b-3ca5-45f0-bade-539c76c0b89e\"><b>치매</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-26af1605-176f-4e7a-a96c-1018ceaee925\">는 명확히 구분할 필요가 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ce3afbbd-f787-4439-befc-544637a70bf1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b9d7532b-4197-4bd7-80ef-5e51a85b4b2a\"><u>건망증은 일시적인 기억력 저하에 불과하지만, </u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e8e6eca2-7c13-40b3-9cf1-9d86514797d4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-186faa67-561d-47ff-9fbe-85f70d80ff30\"><u>치매는 뇌 기능이 전반적으로 떨어져 일상생활에 큰 영향을 주는 질환입니다.</u></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bfe9d987-5b2c-4c72-afc7-f5b31e6e1dea\"><u>​</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-c167d221-9184-4df2-8eb7-680a0082c21e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8186f049-1141-4bde-9f27-4549680cc552\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-8186f049-1141-4bde-9f27-4549680cc552\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b71b3864665c73c4.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b71b3864665c73c4.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b71b3864665c73c4.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-8186f049-1141-4bde-9f27-4549680cc552\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-d795c648-cc1c-449a-958e-4c9762e649bd\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_postit\" id=\"SE-307d0b24-8c2c-4e84-b284-a59180669111\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_postit\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8eb150ba-6b60-4506-ab87-4f14ce02b3fe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b3dd8359-95ff-48a3-bc69-ede21d41729d\"><b>건망증과 치매의 차이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-780a392a-1f80-4284-a999-bf0a292ec39d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-13bbe43f-8885-4a63-a0eb-a96fe9d5d629\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f342a77e-ac17-4208-81c5-2c0d89873263\"><b>건망증</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a2c8a681-34c4-4846-a878-26109944a1a2\">: 기억을 떠올리는 속도가 느려질 뿐, 힌트를 주면 생각이 납니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5344b3a0-018e-495a-8ab8-23b71a1c3e1b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1e36eba3-c286-49f6-9515-1b393be476ee\">예를 들어, 친구 이름이 바로 안 떠오르더라도 얼굴을 보면 곧 기억나는 경우입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-660da428-3c99-4d37-ad5b-05ea7a8de816\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f478b162-93e2-4f05-98cd-ecadb5f8559b\"><b>치매</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f400944f-500d-44c7-9c5c-957fc7e1030c\">: 힌트를 줘도 기억이 나지 않거나, 기억 자체가 사라집니다. 게다가 판단력, 언어 능력, 공간 인지 등 다른 인지 기능에도 문제가 동반됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0d77d660-6cd9-483e-8d15-7a5a264ab5eb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9a9f53c0-7aff-4c06-80f7-7a2bbc2ed89b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d23fdeb6-3d53-45b8-9023-a78c23dad8af\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummyeongjo   \" id=\"SE-04bb28cc-73a9-49be-8b75-9e76b6caab3b\"><i>즉, 건망증은 뇌가 ‘느리게’ 작동하는 것이고, </i></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2403546b-234d-45d8-8f6e-e7642f8cd324\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummyeongjo   \" id=\"SE-29d76f4b-e973-4c91-a287-1e7bc220f1c3\"><i>치매는 뇌 기능이 ‘손상’된 상태입니다.</i></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-780a392a-1f80-4284-a999-bf0a292ec39d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-61fe6943-fd2f-4583-b73d-02c4b3f18da5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_postit\" id=\"SE-a77b8d58-328d-4542-982b-4a41a07d002a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_postit\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7d28a259-43cb-4f98-9ca9-0cf295ef8955\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f8e791e2-4184-4b45-b641-49dab53a52ff\"><b>치매 예방의 핵심 비법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8d7d9d06-e456-4936-a1b7-c713ab619e22\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e4c77fe7-021f-4e0d-a547-29a5f29c0cbc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-25880509-342c-48de-ab09-082e0f439464\"><b>1. 혈관 건강 지키기</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ff3d8386-b275-4b34-816b-2a11d6eea594\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5a55d2a8-68a8-4c4c-9678-93dcf48ee713\">한의학에서는 뇌를 건강하게 하려면 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2fe2e5a5-def3-43e4-81e9-0047b14c1ffb\"><b>혈액이 원활히 흐르는 것</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-96136b61-abf9-4697-ae2d-1cd553500fd1\">이 가장 중요하다고 봅니다. 뇌로 가는 혈류가 막히면 기억력 저하, 어지럼증, 집중력 감소가 쉽게 나타납니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e2a54c38-b2f3-4516-97f1-b40cd4437ea4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f877ac90-3481-41dc-8263-1647503385e9\">매일 30분 이상 걷기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-397bf2a1-68ee-4fa0-8eb0-819d3699db2d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a9c639b7-4b5b-41c0-b986-5f19a09eafe2\">목·어깨 스트레칭으로 긴장 완화</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a81868b2-4f2f-4581-b880-56cc2ebaadd1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c8615965-9155-4b52-b975-50ffca2a1d7a\">과도한 음주와 흡연 줄이기</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-01771b06-707f-4868-a4f5-1e61288dde5d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-547e46e8-0bfd-489d-ae40-bbb5f6c43b5b\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9ce5a3ac-e644-4862-b7b4-6d521deef82f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-967f4d5c-4c03-47a3-9f25-4ab840420dae\"><b>2. 두뇌를 깨우는 활동</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bed39ce8-55ec-4573-88c8-9fa601e26a3c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7f903d4c-a827-4766-a577-4da39ecafd91\">뇌는 쓰지 않으면 기능이 떨어집니다. 새로운 자극을 꾸준히 주면 신경세포 연결이 강화됩니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e75cddb2-79fa-4284-9bda-6b0a00e1eee3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-987e24cc-aa4f-46ea-991f-a4708512fd6c\">책 읽기, 글쓰기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-decaf459-d059-489f-99c3-8a10e62e6d37\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ac71c9c7-552a-4db6-931d-39aa9f3fda6e\">악기 연주, 새로운 취미 배우기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6831149d-7f93-4710-a7cc-87babb113f39\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-394f6107-291b-451d-a0ee-fcd46ee3668b\">사람들과 대화 자주 나누기</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4afe1cea-496f-49df-b323-533c1efe2b21\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9a2d27e8-dc1f-459f-bc3f-32689bf55715\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c6114a79-01bc-4b2f-96f3-6eea50cbf9fd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6bfea7b0-6af4-4fd5-98a9-22a793864ea1\"><b>3. 올바른 식습관</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-545fa4b3-9008-4037-90c0-e74bbe1b5bfa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aabf4e5f-28e9-4cf7-819c-000b887bf8cd\">뇌 건강에 좋은 음식은 꾸준히 섭취하고, 해로운 음식은 피하는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a68f5554-53e3-4965-9088-d22844980ab3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-81d93075-e658-4e12-9b45-5928412a0525\">좋은 음식: 견과류, 등푸른 생선, 채소, 해조류</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1c98960c-802b-48ee-a557-788f5430d7ba\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-88201b8b-6974-43ff-a95d-b084c4631199\">피해야 할 음식: 기름지고 가공된 음식, 과도한 설탕</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-21b6078e-36c9-4dec-9cb9-810bb36a4f19\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-935addde-d7af-48d1-9b3d-6b024bab73f7\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ffe99df2-1d54-4c44-a0e8-cbbfea46d691\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a250c978-d9d6-43c8-81b1-4ba2492eacb3\"><b>4. 숙면 습관</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-034b6898-705f-4158-96bc-8981d1d2a00f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-19152279-0959-4de6-84f4-64c29387d863\">수면 중 뇌 속 노폐물이 정리됩니다. 하루 7시간 내외의 숙면은 기억력 유지에 큰 도움이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-8d7d9d06-e456-4936-a1b7-c713ab619e22\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-comp