/div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b5c42342-504d-4c3d-8c8d-00099de69b92\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-24e00e7e-2fd4-4660-987d-00ccd531cdd4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummyeongjo   \" id=\"SE-0220bf42-8225-4e20-b5ca-bd1297128708\"><b>한방 치료로 뇌 건강 지키기</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-51577d37-0fac-4a08-abfe-542b4eb65726\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummyeongjo   \" id=\"SE-a4a6bc67-ceb9-499f-b13a-116f69183dce\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-597c8130-785c-4e86-bafe-adddc09c67a4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d18ed509-31d0-49b9-8418-cd410f1e401f\">한의학에서는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0bcaf820-5868-4008-adfb-b2028ac20cd9\"><b>침, 뜸, 한약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-db6a5d55-5fa6-488f-930f-0d2ac856f2c6\"> 등을 활용해 뇌혈류를 개선하고, 기억력·집중력을 높이는 치료를 합니다. 체질에 맞춘 맞춤 한약은 뇌 기능 저하 속도를 늦추는 데 도움이 될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-b5c42342-504d-4c3d-8c8d-00099de69b92\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" 