t-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aba21a6f-b274-4d00-aabb-bc25f62f56b7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-de45b1a6-a86d-4daa-8f18-9e3159001736\">중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9cbcec82-26f2-406c-bd2d-0c26759f91d8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3d00fe1b-1a7f-4c3d-ba22-3e9c85358728\">이수한의원에서는 개인의 체질과 건강 상태를 종합적으로 분석해, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-65351174-aaa9-48b0-9608-6d4c8507716e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-45b4d01d-200c-46d7-ad68-0a9a2be0dfaa\">뇌혈류 개선과 인지 기능 강화를 돕는 맞춤 한방 치료를 제공합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ebbe33e7-1f4f-4207-b892-a0a68727ea4f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-03bfea32-9292-48e7-b3c1-92e2599bba22\">오늘부터 작은 습관으로 건강한 두뇌를 지켜나가세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c30b4bbd-bb7d-4a0d-802c-10c10970e348\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummyeongjo   \" id=\"SE-1ef7cbc8-a822-47bc-b0f4-1b46416bcfb8\"><i><b>​</b></i></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-f780acf4-6222-4bc9-9de9-d5b9f66156e7\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-center se-l-default\" >\n          